2780179541508827126.Text: An Orc named Ra'Gruzgob seems to think he is a Khajiit. He asked me about his tail -- he hasn't got one, of course -- I said it looked fine. This seemed to please him. It's a funny old world, all right.

2643516333650128096.Text: Ra'Gruzgob told me that he found something I would like. He put it under his pillow.
